Interface ValueExportExtension<V extends Value>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FreebaseExportExtension, SimpleIdExportExtension, StringIdExportExtension

    public interface ValueExportExtension<V extends Value>
    Classes that implement this interface export additional data for snaks with certain values.

    Markus Kroetzsch

                        throws org.openrdf.rio.RDFHandlerException
        Writes additional RDF data for the given data.
        Parameters:
        resource - the subject for which to write the data
        propertyIdValue - the property that was used for writing
        value - the value used with the property
        rdfWriter - the writer to write the data to
        owlDeclarationBuffer - the buffer to write necessary vocabulary declarations to
        Throws:
        org.openrdf.rio.RDFHandlerException - if the data could not be written
